ps modernization play on a 47yr-tenured single-RPLS surveying firm in Wichita Falls:  (1) drone/UAV survey program (~25-40% labor savings on topo + as-built); (2) 3D laser scanning + reality capture for as-built and infrastructure work; (3) online project portal for ALTA / FEMA / boundary client self-service; (4) RTK GPS base station network for sub-cm field productivity; (5) automated CAD/drafting workflow + AI plat-review. Plausible 1.5-2× EBITDA path 18-24 months. Off-market multiple 3-5× EBITDA in current LOW-PE-attention environment; would shift to 5-7× as ETA/search-fund deal-velocity ramps 2026-2027.', 'medium', 0.45),
